Package sndlib.ext.generators.gml

Class Summary
BaseGmlProperties Base implementation of the GML properties used in SNDlib.
GmlCoordinatesFromNodeProvider Simple implementation of the GmlCoordinatesProvider interface.
GmlStyles This class collects some style constants which can be addressed in the GML property settings.
GmlStyles.LinkStyle Collects some link style constants.
GmlStyles.LinkWidth Collects some link width constants.
GmlStyles.NodeShape Collects some node shape constants.
ProblemGmlGenerator This class generates a GML document for a given Problem.
ProblemGmlProperties This class collects the properties to be used when generating a GML for a Problem.
SNDlibGmlGenerator This class provides a simple interface for generating GMLs for Problems and SolvedProblems.
SNDlibGmlProperties This class aggregates the ProblemGmlProperties and the SolutionGmlProperties.
SolutionGmlGenerator This class generates a GML document for a given SolvedProblem.
SolutionGmlProperties This class collects the properties to be used when generating a GML for a SolvedProblem.
SolutionGmlProperties.Defaults Default property values.
 

Enum Summary
SolutionGmlProperties.GradientType Enumerates the available gradient types.
